Usage: createUserBundleNet [-help] <name> -nets <net>+
                           -object1 <inst|hInst|term|term|group>
                           -object2 <inst|hInst|term|term|group>

-help                                     # Prints out the command usage
<name>                                    # Bundle Nets Name (string, required)
-nets <net>+                              # Nets List ((net)+, required)
-object1 <inst|hInst|term|term|group>     # Object Name
                                          # ((inst|hInst|term|term|group), required)
-object2 <inst|hInst|term|term|group>     # Object Name
                                          # ((inst|hInst|term|term|group), required)